Interface ResetableIterator<T extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ResetableIterator<T>

    @InterfaceAudience.Public
@InterfaceStability.Stable
public interface ResetableIterator<T extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable>
extends ResetableIterator<T>
    This defines an interface to a stateful Iterator that can replay elements added to it directly. Note that this does not extend Iterator.
